---
title: Easy Coconut & Lemongrass Beef Noodles with Crispy Shallots
description: The star of this sumptuous noodle number is our Sri Lankan spice blend; it's fused with creamy coconut milk and ginger
lemongrass paste to give it a mild, yet tangy flavour that everyone will enjoy. A perfect balance of easy and tasty, we reckon you’ll
be losing the local takeaway joint's number the moment you've tried it.
